[[File:Theodore Herzl.jpg|thumb|upright=1.2|right|[[Theodor Herzl]] is considered the founder of the Modern Zionist movement. In his 1896 book ''[[Der Judenstaat]]'', he envisioned the founding of a future independent Jewish state during the 20th century.]]
